Year: Men'S Tennisjune 29, 2023Young Adds Six To 2023 Recruiting Classafter Completing His First Season As Head Coach, Geoff Young Ushered In Year Two Of His Tenure By Announcing The Addition Of Six New Players In The Class Of 2023-24: Alexander Ekstrand, Aleksa Krivokapic, Soham Purohit, Stefan Simeunovic, Juan David Velasquez And Henrik Villanger.
